Package com.tangosol.util.function

Class Remote

java.lang.Object
com.tangosol.util.function.Remote
public class Remote extends Object
Helper interfaces and methods that enable capture of standard JDK functional interfaces as serializable lambdas.
Since:
12.2.1
Author:
as 2014.07.16
